snippet.title: The Sims 3 Movie Stuff Trailer -- Part 3
snippet.description:
Set the stage with The Sims 3 Movie Stuff and tell more unique stories with décor, furnishings, and clothing inspired by iconic movie genres. 

Whether you're creating a caped crusader or an über-villain, your Sim is going to look absolutely super in a range of tight-fitting, over-the-top costumes.

Cast your Sims in The Sims 3 Movie Stuff. http://thesims.com/en-us/the-sims-3#!stuffpack/the-sims-3-movie-stuff
